BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 174.96 750 Td (YOUR RIGHTS UNDER IDEA - PLAIN LANGUAGE) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 0.5 w 72 738 m 540 738 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 710 Td (1. FREE APPROPRIATE PUBLIC EDUCATION \(FAPE\) - Your child deserves) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 696 Td (   a free education designed to meet their unique needs.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 682 Td (2. EVALUATION - You can request an evaluation at any time. The school) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 668 Td (   must respond within their state timeline.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 654 Td (3. PARTICIPATION - You are an EQUAL member of the IEP team. Your) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 640 Td (   input matters as much as any professional's.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 626 Td (4. INFORMED CONSENT - Nothing happens without your written permission.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 612 Td (5. PRIOR WRITTEN NOTICE - School must tell you IN WRITING before) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 598 Td (   changing \(or refusing to change\) your child's services.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 584 Td (6. LEAST RESTRICTIVE ENVIRONMENT - Your child should be with) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 570 Td (   non-disabled peers to the maximum extent appropriate.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 556 Td (7. DISPUTE RESOLUTION - You can disagree! Options: mediation,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 542 Td (   due process hearing, state complaint.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 528 Td (8. STAY PUT - During disputes, child stays in current placement.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 514 Td (9. INDEPENDENT EVALUATION - You can get an outside evaluation) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 500 Td (   at district expense if you disagree with theirs.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 486 Td (10. TRANSFER OF RIGHTS - At 18, rights transfer to student.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
